This application reads and writes the programming of live fuel-tank monitoring consoles.
That programming governs leak detection and regulatory compliance. It is intended for
trained service technicians working on equipment they are authorised to service. You are
responsible for backing up a console before writing to it, for keeping the rollback file
the tool creates, and for verifying the console's programming and leak-detection operation
after any write.


